  39,8,When uman exista întrista el implora his Domnitor sincerely devotat catre Him! as devreme as El binecuvânta him el uita his anterior implora situa idol rândui DUMNEZEU divert others His poteca! spune Enjoy vostri disbelief temporarily; tu crea hellfire
